{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "35ce110c-df54-45ce-b7a3-46906653b6bc",
    "name": "[EXTERNAL] Xenith APIs",
    "description": "# Welcome to Xenith APIs!\n\nThis Postman Collection provides you easy access to Xenith API products, from Balances, Pay Ins, and Pay Outs.\n\n## Get Started\n\n1. Create a Xenith account\n    \n2. Log in to your Xenith account\n    \n3. Visit [Developer Settings page](https://app.staging.xenithpay.com/developer-settings) to generate API keys. Store both the secret and access key securely\n    \n4. Create a new Postman environment with the following variables: `secret_key` and `access_key`, and [<code>uri</code>](https://docs.xenithpay.com/docs/environments)\n    \n5. This postman collection has a pre-script built-in in Scripts section to generate signature automatically to access Xenith's APIs. All you need is to provide the value of `secret_key`, `access_key`, and `uri` correctly in the Environment variable\n    \n6. Make your first API call by hitting one of the APIs provided in this collection!",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "48445734",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/48445734-35ce110c-df54-45ce-b7a3-46906653b6bc?source=collection_link"
  },
